title: Doc HoneyBerry Kitty Surgery
description: Doc HoneyBerry Kitty Surgery is a simulation game where you play as Doc HoneyBerry to help this cute little kitty from the crash. Take care of the injuries and heal the broken bones. After recovery, dress up the kitty with many styles and colors of clothes, pants, shoes, hats, and different pattern skins. Give the kitty a cute makeover!
